				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$A_0$$\end{document} with measurable biomarkers, it provides a quantitative framework for personalized treatment decisions that could optimize resource allocation in diabetic wound care58.

To better understand the impact of aging on wound healing, we developed a predictive mathematical model that defines an individual’s biological age using two key parameters: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
